{"id":158806,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/德国之声-也门出现权力真空/","date":"2011-06-07T16:35:05Z","modified":"2011-06-07T16:35:05Z","title":"德国之声 | 也门出现权力真空","content":"<div>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">萨那</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">萨利赫总统出境后，也门国内暴力依旧。据当地媒体报道，周二（</span><span>6</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月</span><span>7</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">日），在塔伊斯市（</span><span>Tais</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">），共和卫队和反政府人士之间再度发生交火，在首都萨那的阿尔哈萨巴区，发现１０具男尸，死者身份不明。过去数周，当地一再发生政府军与一名部落首领的武装分子之间的战斗。该部落首领支持示威青年。萨利赫总统上周五在总统府附近一座清真寺遇袭受伤，后飞往邻国沙特治疗，迄今呆在该国一座医院内。萨利赫强调，一旦痊愈就会回国执政。数月来要求萨利赫下台的示威运动和反对派则宣布将全力予以制止。</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15136568%2C00.html&#038;title=%E4%B9%9F%E9%97%A8%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E6%9D%83%E5%8A%9B%E7%9C%9F%E7%A9%BA\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"738338\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}